                            <p>Experience the breathtaking beauty of nature's grandest formations</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="pics/2.png" alt="Forest Path" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="carousel-content">
                            <h3>Enchanted Forest</h3>
                            <p>Wander through mystical pathways surrounded by ancient trees</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="pics/3.jpg" alt="Ocean Waves" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="carousel-content">
                            <h3>Ocean Serenity</h3>
                            <p>Feel the calming rhythm of waves meeting pristine shores</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="pics/4.jpg" alt="Desert Dunes" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="carousel-content">
                            <h3>Desert Dreams</h3>
                            <p>Explore the golden sands and endless horizons</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button class="carousel-control prev" aria-label="Previous">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                        <path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control next" aria-label="Next">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                        <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    </svg>
